      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que la série de terme général $\\Arctan(n+a) - \\Arctan n$ est\n    convergente.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que la série de terme général <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\Arctan(n+a) - \\Arctan n\\)</span> est convergente.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "bc7353bc-f485-457a-aa69-38b6a4b70d0d",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\sim \\frac a{n^2}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sim \\frac a{n^2}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "e9645b81-f757-4f18-afac-f61c987b1eed",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "On pose $S(a) = \\sum_{k=0}^\\infty (\\Arctan(k+a) - \\Arctan k)$.\n    Trouver $\\lim_{a\\to+\\infty} S(a)$.",
        "html": "<p>On pose <span class=\"math inline\">\\(S(a) = \\sum_{k=0}^\\infty (\\Arctan(k+a) - \\Arctan k)\\)</span>. Trouver <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\lim_{a\\to+\\infty} S(a)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "94d70288-dc4f-433d-be95-e3f0cf08a4e4",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$S(a) \\ge \\sum_{k=0}^n \\Arctan(k+a)-\\Arctan k \\to\n              \\frac\\pi2 + \\Arctan 1 + \\Arctan\\frac12 + \\dots\n              + \\Arctan\\frac1n\n               \\Rightarrow  S(a) \\to +\\infty$ lorsque $a\\to+\\infty$ .",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(S(a) \\ge \\sum_{k=0}^n \\Arctan(k+a)-\\Arctan k \\to\n              \\frac\\pi2 + \\Arctan 1 + \\Arctan\\frac12 + \\dots\n              + \\Arctan\\frac1n\n               \\Rightarrow  S(a) \\to +\\infty\\)</span> lorsque <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a\\to+\\infty\\)</span> .</p>\n"
      }
